---
permalink: "/docs.html"
layout: base.njk
title: "Component overview"
showcaseCss: true
extraHead: |
  <style>
    .dc-wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 32px; }
    .dc-lead { font-size: 16px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 0 48px; }
    .dc-section-title { font-size: 24px; margin: 64px 0 24px; }
    .dc-token-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
    .dc-token { border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-md); background: var(--q2w-surface); overflow: hidden; }
    .dc-token__swatch { height: 72px; }
    .dc-token__meta { padding: 10px 12px; }
    .dc-token__name { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--q2w-text); }
    .dc-token__val { font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }
    .dc-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    .ln-showcase__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      grid-auto-rows: 280px;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .ln-card {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      border: 1px solid var(--q2w-border);
      border-radius: var(--q2w-radius-md);
      background: var(--q2w-surface);
      overflow: hidden;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .ln-card:hover { border-color: var(--q2w-accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 2; }
    .ln-card__preview {
      position: relative;
      flex: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      --q2w-surface: #ffffff;
      --q2w-surface-soft: #f7f8fa;
      --q2w-text: #1b2230;
      --q2w-text-muted: #5b6577;
      --q2w-text-faint: #8a93a3;
      --q2w-border: #dde1e7;
      --q2w-accent-soft: #e6f3f2;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2f7, #dbe3ec);
    }
    .ln-card__meta { padding: 14px 18px; border-top: 1px solid var(--q2w-border); }
    .ln-card__name { font-family: var(--q2w-font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: var(--q2w-accent); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .ln-card__desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--q2w-text-muted); line-height: 1.45; }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .ln-showcase__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 2; }
      .dc-token-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .ln-showcase__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ln-card--lg { grid-column: span 1; }
      .dc-token-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .dc-wrap { padding: 40px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
---

{% include "nav-docs.njk" %}

<main class="dc-wrap">
  <h1 style="font-size: 48px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 16px;">Components</h1>
  <p class="dc-lead">
    All 25+ q2w-mapcss components. Click any card to see live preview, usage, modifiers, and copy-paste markup.
  </p>

  <div id="quick-start">
    {% include "quickstart-section.njk" %}
  </div>

  <h2 id="templates" class="dc-section-title">Templates</h2>
  <p class="dc-note">
    Need more than a single snippet? Start from these ready-made app shells under <code>snippets/templates/</code>.
  </p>
  <div class="dc-token-grid">
    <div class="dc-token">
      <div class="dc-token__meta">
        <div class="dc-token__name">basic.html</div>
        <div class="dc-token__val">Floating header + map + footer shell</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dc-token">
      <div class="dc-token__meta">
        <div class="dc-token__name">with-panel.html</div>
        <div class="dc-token__val">Map shell with interactive layer panel binding</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dc-token">
      <div class="dc-token__meta">
        <div class="dc-token__name">dashboard.html</div>
        <div class="dc-token__val">Map plus dashboard sidebar layout</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="tokens" class="dc-section-title">Tokens</h2>
  <p class="dc-note">q2w-mapcss exposes themeable design tokens through the <code>--q2w-*</code> prefix. Use them to align your export chrome, legends, and overlays without editing generated qgis2web JavaScript.</p>
  <div class="dc-token-grid">
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:#0f7a78;"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-accent</div><div class="dc-token__val">Primary accent</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:#ffffff;"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-surface</div><div class="dc-token__val">Default surface</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:#f7f8fa;"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-surface-soft</div><div class="dc-token__val">Soft panels and cards</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:#1b2230;"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-text</div><div class="dc-token__val">Primary text</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--q2w-seq-1),var(--q2w-seq-6));"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-seq-*</div><div class="dc-token__val">Sequential choropleth palette</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--q2w-div-1),var(--q2w-div-5));"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">--q2w-div-*</div><div class="dc-token__val">Diverging palette</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:#0f1520;"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">data-theme="dark"</div><div class="dc-token__val">Dark preset</div></div></div>
    <div class="dc-token"><div class="dc-token__swatch" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d6fc4,#2f7d4a,#d8632a,#3f4a5c);"></div><div class="dc-token__meta"><div class="dc-token__name">Theme presets</div><div class="dc-token__val">Ocean, forest, sunset, slate</div></div></div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="dc-section-title">Components</h2>
  <div class="ln-showcase__grid">
    {% for component in components %}
      <a href="docs/{{ component.slug }}.html" class="ln-card{% if component.slug == 'header' or component.slug == 'footer' %} ln-card--lg{% endif %}">
        <div class="ln-card__preview">
          {% include component.preview %}
        </div>
        <div class="ln-card__meta">
          <div class="ln-card__name">{{ component.tag }}</div>
          <div class="ln-card__desc">{{ component.title }}</div>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>

{% include "footer.njk" %}
